  "note": [
    {
      "text": "Three-port laparoscopic approach (umbilical 12 mm, suprapubic 5 mm, left lower quadrant 5 mm). Veress needle insufflation to 15 mmHg. Appendix found gangrenous with visible perforation at distal tip. Mesoappendix divided with vascular endoscopic stapler. Appendiceal base secured and transected with endoscopic stapler. Specimen removed in endoscopic retrieval bag through umbilical port. Estimated blood loss 50 mL. OR time 68 minutes."
    }
